 22/3/18 Red Lodg Awaken at 3 a.m. by a loud and heavi bombard and by the adjac heavi batteri fire hard . Most of the stuff come over was German and land heavili around Prows Point and the Hyde Park corner . It seem that they raid the 21st post and the most contradictori report are to hand here . Some say that 5,6,7,8 9 post were raid and that our casualti are not light . Went down to the A.D.L. at breakfast time and saw Dr Simmond who say he has had onli a few wound through and they say onli 5 6 were raid . Howev there is a good fog this morn and the 21st should be abl to look round and to see exact how thing stand . Abercrombi was forward
